## Quick Start: Local Development

Create `frontend/.env.local` (not committed):

```bash
# API Configuration
REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1
REACT_APP_ENVIRONMENT=development

# Feature Flags
REACT_APP_AI_ASSISTANT_ENABLED=true
```

Then: `npm start`

## Environment-Specific API URLs

The app **auto-detects** from domain, but you can override:

- **Dev:** `https://dev-backend.meatscentral.com/api/v1`
- **UAT:** `https://uat.meatscentral.com/api/v1`
- **Prod:** `https://meatscentral.com/api/v1`
- **Local:** `http://localhost:8000/api/v1`

